11. Income Taxes
Components of Income from Continuing Operations Before Income Taxes
As a result of the Redomiciliation Transaction on April 4, 2018, the following references to domestic activities represent the U.S. for fiscal years
2019 and 2018 and Singapore for fiscal year 2017. The following table presents the components of income from continuing operations before income
taxes for financial reporting purposes:
 Fiscal Year
 2019 2018 2017
 (In millions)
